        *************
        limits
        *************
        |travis-ci| |coveralls| |pypi| |license|
        
        *limits* provides utilities to implement rate limiting using
        various strategies and storage backends such as redis & memcached.
        
        Read more at `readthedocs <http://limits.readthedocs.org>`_
        
        
        
        .. :changelog:
        
        Changelog
        ---------
        
        1.0.1 2015-01-08
        ================
        * Example usage in docs.
        
        1.0.0 2015-01-08
        ================
        * Initial import of common rate limiting code from `Flask-Limiter <https://github.com/alisaifee/flask-limiter`
        
        
